{"tid":1592053,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普推謝四做接班人","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:21:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3860467e80d226a6cc63acdcbb0f636737b9a13e","tid":1592053,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】英超利物浦領隊高普認為，神奇隊長謝拉特會是理想中的接班人。<br />\n<br />\n前利物浦隊長謝拉特（Steven Gerrard）現時執教格拉斯哥流浪，已多次公開表示，終有一天會回歸任教前東家。<br />\n<br />\n「如果紅軍明日炒我，杜格利殊或者是取代我的第一人選，但最有可能仍是由格流挖角謝拉特。」德國籍主帥高普接受雜誌《442》訪問時表示。<br />\n<br />\n「如果你問我意見，我會說謝拉特是繼承者，他需要我幫忙的話，任何時間我都願意出手。」這名合約直至2022年的紅軍主帥續說：「我不是天才，不完美，但會付出100%。我不是妒忌的人，如果有人需要我幫忙，我一定會幫。」<br />\n<br />\n39歲的謝拉特踢而優則教，帶領格流75場，取得44勝20和11負，目標是推倒些路迪的蘇超霸權。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"9bdabd1f419ba0d26f42d8dcf99df6cb179a6c19","tid":1592053,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"c3e5d946f62303b0b7177faa2ff9d39b534389f0","tid":1592053,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/mnu18dbY9tSFiS0srz/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fmnu18dbY9tSFiS0srz%2Fgiphy.gif&h=ed34e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/TEn28LakEth1cquMj6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FTEn28LakEth1cquMj6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=cfe82f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f71b07a7608eb355652e236c51e701fc1d1e587","tid":1592053,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:18:14.000